: SIGNED	DUP 32767 > IF 65536 - THEN ;	\ <16b> --- <n>

: CWMOVE	5 CMOVE ; 			\ <addr1> <addr> --- <>
: CW@		COUNT >< >R C@  R> OR  SIGNED ;	\ <addr> --- <n>
: CW!		>R  DUP >< R@ C!  R> 1+ C! ;	\ <n> <addr> --- <>

: CW,		DUP  8 RSHIFT C,  C, ;		\ <n> --- <> Big endian 16 bit
: CW+!		DUP >R CW@ +  R> CW! ;		\ <n> <addr> --- <>
